w accredited by AACSB   International  the principle accrediting body for business programs in the world  As a wholly undergraduate program  VMI is among a very select group of schools that have achieved this distinction  The John W  and Jane M  Roberts American Free Enterprise Program is made possible because of the unswerving support of Mr  and Mrs  Roberts  founders of the Solite Corporation  Established in the department in 1998  the program supports  2 Institute Professorships The John W  and Jane M  Roberts Institute Professorship in Free Enterprise Economics The John W  and Jane M  Roberts Institute Professorship in Free Enterprise Business The John W  and Jane M  Roberts Lecture Series Departmental Internships Funds for Faculty and Cadet Research Resources for Departmental Awards In recognition of the important role that Mr  and Mrs  Roberts have played in our department  our highest award for cadet achievement  the Roberts Medal Academic Achievement Award is presented each year to the top ranking cadet in the graduating class  The award consists of a medal and a cash prize Information   Social Sciences Economics   Business Home Degrees   Programs Courses Economics Newsletter Departmental Activities Awards Cadet Investment Group EC BU Internship Program McDowell Scholarship Free Enterprise Program Beta Gamma Sigma Omicron Delta Epsilon BRIDGE VMI Service Club Policies   Forms About ECBU Faculty Open House Presentation Senior Exit Survey Alumni  97    07 survey Donna Potter Executive Secretary P   540  464 7234 F   540  464 7005 Virginia Military Institute 345 Scott Shipp Hall Lexington  VA  24450 Contact ECBU  Information   Social Sciences Economics   Business Home Degrees   Programs Courses Economics Newsletter Departmental Activities Awards Cadet Investment Group EC BU Internship Program McDowell Scholarship Free Enterprise Program Beta Gamma Sigma Omicron Delta Epsilon BRIDGE VMI Service Club Policies   Forms About ECBU Faculty Open House Presentation Sen